<Link id="l01315" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1315"><Highlight kind="normal">  </Highlight><Highlight kind="comment">// though the public class spawns a new &#39;impl&#39; instance for each load,</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01316" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1316"><Highlight kind="normal">  </Highlight><Highlight kind="comment">// they share a single memory manager.  This can become a problem when page</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01317" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1317"><Highlight kind="normal">  </Highlight><Highlight kind="comment">// permissions are applied.</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>
